0x88CD646F.name: MUMBLE_REMOVE_VOICE_TARGET_PLAYER

params.name: targetId
params.description: A Mumble voice target ID, ranging from 1..30 (inclusive).

params.name: player
params.description: The player index to remove from the target.

0x88CD646F.description:
Removes the specified player from the user's voice targets.

Performs the opposite operation of [MUMBLE_ADD_VOICE_TARGET_PLAYER](#\_0x32C5355A)
